{"tid":1548353,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"將「港人治港，高度自治」加入口號及文宣","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T12:56:49.000Z","uid":80363,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fbff030b8cc8fd7835e181c632949c941ef12217","tid":1548353,"uid":80363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"懶人包：將「港人治港，高度自治」加入口號及文宣，以令反送中運動昇華為自治運動，而其港人高度自治權是當年聯合聲明北京當局所承諾及基本法所授予的基本憲制權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景：隨住特衰宣佈撤回送中，反送中運動感覺上開始失焦失民氣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n受各巴打啟發：<br />\n<br />\n第一位巴打：<br />\n美國國會提晒水：香港人需要向世界宣告──這是一場香港自治運動 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543035\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543035</a>。<br />\n<br />\n第二巴打：<br />\n澳洲不需要從英女皇獨立，香港亦不需要。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547974\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547974</a>。<br />\n<br />\n推論：<br />\n本人認為我地需要將運動昇華為自治運動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一黎，第一位巴打所講，美國已經提哂水，我地要有實質行動，就係將「港人治港，高度自治」加入口號及宣傳，比美國出師有名，名正言順咁推《人權與民主法案》。推左呢條法案之後可以令賣港既政客其政治成本大幅上升，未來甚至可以令以美國為首嘅西方國家（歐盟）推呢條法案。《人權法案》係重中之重，9月8號一定要逼爆美領同嗌呢個口號。<br />\n<br />\n二黎，回應番第二位巴打，如果我地有真正自治，其實名義上跟邊個國家都冇所謂，有實無名點都好過無實無名。再重申一點，我地依家唔係爭取要更多嘅自治權，而係爭取返我哋本身應有嘅憲法所授予我地既基本自治權利。<br />\n<br />\n三黎，將「港人治港，高度自治」加入口號及宣傳可以重新聚焦運動，亦都可以促使政府回應五大訴求！而雙真普選正正係呢句口號所劍指。<br />\n<br />\n最後，真係要將呢號口號嗌出黎同埋加入文宣，最好有埋英文版（Hong Kong People, Ruling Hong Kong)(Real Autonomy, True Democracy! )。文宣個方面可以以香港回歸後自治權不斷萎縮，點樣不斷影響民生為切入點，而爭取番本身應有既自治權可以令我地香港人既生活更好，呢一點可以拉攏藍絲、老一輩既支持：(呢個fb page講左好多重點，新移民、房屋、醫療etc...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/406156242829341/posts/1991480190963597?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F406156242829341%2Fposts%2F1991480190963597%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=990cdc96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/406156242829341/posts/1991480190963597?sfns=mo</a><br />\n)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReal Autonomy, True Democracy! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHong Kong People, Ruling Hong Kong!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港人治港，高度自治!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a225ce3eaff42587143ff4ec3f786487f9003e","tid":1548353,"uid":80363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6b6bae2447e87f2975306f5a95851f5011b0f4","tid":1548353,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">麻煩出去幫手推哂908 既post上黎，我P牌推唔到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">九月八日 聽日呀！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1:30pm遮打 ----&gt;  2pm<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國領事館</span></span> </span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">為美國風災祈禱：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n颶風「多里安」<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逼近美國東岸在巴哈馬導致20人死亡</span></span>- <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478908-20190905.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478908-20190905.htm&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=377e9d28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478908-20190905.htm&h=531c3329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478908-20190905.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2019/09/05/b6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde0