br />\n呢句係之前唔知邊個領導人（鄧小平？）講過<br />\n意思係指佢同北京當局作出過承諾。<br />\n但呢加呢個承諾左既自治係不斷萎縮。<br />\n嗌呢個口號就出師有名。<br />\n最少爭取番一開始聯合聲明同基本法授予我地呢個程度既自治權which is <br />\n巴打所講<br />\n「只要行政長官等所有官員同所有立法會議員都係由真正選擇之普選產生，只要做足聯合聲明同基本法承諾之自治，即除國防外交外，其餘事務一概由香港自治；<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港名義上是否歸屬中国、抑或中國、美國、英國、獨立不獨立，絕對不值得執著。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n但港人治港 完全自治係冇一個領導人講過，咁我地嗌就出師無名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424761599e029698c4d5f40ee0c4ab5a32193465","tid":1548353,"uid":80363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e195b4344673d3ee4bc1f0ce912219ad828cd7f","tid":1548353,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港人治港，<span style=\"color: red;\">民主</span>自治</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"呢個都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65982af2298c49bd8d5b60b3bb678defcab264f2","tid":1548353,"uid":80363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"其實唔一定要嗌番exactly 「高度自治」<br />\n<br />\n最緊要個口號係講到我地要應有既自治權同出師有名就ok"},{"pid":"25da576ecd0d8d46f183e4df0029dd47dec8330d","tid":1548353,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"424761599e029698c4d5f40ee0c4ab5a32193465","tid":1548353,"uid":80363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e195b4344673d3ee4bc1f0ce912219ad828cd7f","tid":1548353,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港人治港，<span style=\"color: red;\">民主</span>自治</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"呢個都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"明明就好好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/